title: DDFP 504: Week 9 recap, Midseason QB Rankings & Who will win the AFC North?
itunes:title: DDFP 504: Week 9 recap, Midseason QB Rankings & Who will win the AFC North?
description:
Shek is joined by Ike Taylor, Handsome Hank and Cynthia Frelund to discuss who will win the AFC North and NFC North divisions and whether or not politics get brought up in the locker room. Then, the fellas and Cynthia discuss the best wins and worst losses from Week 9, highlighting the Raiders' win and the Vikings' loss. Plus, Shek and the guys do a re-ranking of the best quarterbacks in the league at the midpoint in the season, as well as choose which QB they'd personally want on their team for the 2017 NFL season.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
